&lt;p&gt;This is a tutorial for an old version of PythonOCC. Download for &lt;a href="https://academy2.ifcopenshell.org/files/ifcopenhouse_space.py"&gt;pythonOCC &amp;lt;= 0.6&lt;/a&gt;  or &lt;a href="https://academy2.ifcopenshell.org/files/ifcopenhouse_space-pythonOCC-0.16.0.py"&gt;pythonOCC 0.16.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>ifcopenshell</category><category>python</category><category>pythonocc</category><guid>https://academy2.ifcopenshell.org/posts/using-ifcopenshell-and-pythonocc-to-construct-new-geometry/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 06 Aug 2020 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>